metadata.Title: CVE-2020-9386 on Ubuntu 14.04 ESM (trusty) - low.
metadata.Description: In Mahara 18.10 before 18.10.5, 19.04 before 19.04.4, and 19.10 before 19.10.2, file metadata information is disclosed to group members in the Elasticsearch result list despite them not having access to that artefact anymore.

criterions.comment: mahara: while related to the CVE in some way, a decision has been made to ignore this issue (note: 'end of standard support').
